  "description": "A funny &amp; surprising tale of love, lying and laundry where charismatic comic Katie-Ellen Humphries (CBC’s The Debaters, OUT-TV) shares her fraught history as a pathological people pleaser - if that’s okay with you. Critic’s Choice pick in Victoria &amp; a “Top Show to See” at both Vancouver &amp; San Diego Fringe Fests.",
